#ROOM
Vnum     43700
Name     &xThe Necropolis Gate&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand at the entrance of the massive floating necropolis of 
Naxxramas. The air is freezing, and the hum of dark 
necromancy vibrates through the stone floor. Four wide 
thoroughfares lead away from this central landing, each 
dedicated to a different quarter of the Scourge's power.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    38563
Desc      Return to the Eastern Plaguelands.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43701
Desc      The Central Hub.~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43701
Name     &xThe Central Hub - Chamber of Shadows&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the lower necropolis. A massive circular hall 
where the four wings of Naxxramas meet. Stone braziers of 
blue frost light the way. To the northwest lies the Arachnid 
Quarter. To the northeast, the Plague Quarter. To the 
southeast, the Military Quarter. To the southwest, the 
Construct Quarter.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43700
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction northeast~
ToRoom    43740
Desc      The Plague Quarter.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction northwest~
ToRoom    43710
Desc      The Arachnid Quarter.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction southeast~
ToRoom    43770
Desc      The Military Quarter.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction southwest~
ToRoom    43810
Desc      The Construct Quarter.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43516 10 43701
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43702
Name     &xThe North Wing Lookout&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone landing offering a view of the 
Plague Quarter from the hub.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43701
Desc      The hub.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43521 5 43702
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43703
Name     &xThe South Wing Lookout&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone landing offering a view of the 
Military Quarter from the hub.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43701
Desc      The hub.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43521 5 43703
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43710
Name     &xThe Arachnid Quarter - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls here are completely covered in thick, sticky webbing. 
Small insects swarm in the dim light, and the air smells 
of ammonia. Anub'Rekhan can be heard clicking his 
mandibles in the chamber ahead.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43711
Desc      The Lair of Anub'Rekhan.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction southeast~
ToRoom    43701
Desc      The central hub.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43531 10 43710
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43711
Name     &xThe Lair of Anub'Rekhan&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide circular hall filled with the remains of former 
intruders. Anub'Rekhan stand in the center, his golden 
armor glinting in the dim light. He summons a swarm 
of locusts to herald your arrival.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43712
Desc      The Widows' Walk.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43710
Desc      The arachnid entry.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43506 1 43711
  Reset G 1 43634 1
Reset M 0 43531 5 43711
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43712
Name     &xThe Widows' Walk&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A long hallway lined with the statues of spider-queens. 
Grand Widow Faerlina stands at the far end, overseeing 
the training of her acolytes. The air is thick with 
the scent of incense and shadow.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43713
Desc      Faerlina's Sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43711
Desc      Anub'Rekhan's lair.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43516 10 43712
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43713
Name     &xThe Sanctum of Grand Widow Faerlina&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber filled with pews and a 
raised stone altar. Faerlina stands before the altar, 
her whip ready to punish any who show weakness. Her 
most loyal followers stand guard in the aisles.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43714
Desc      The Webbed Tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43712
Desc      The widow's walk.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43507 1 43713
  Reset G 1 43631 1
Reset M 0 43516 10 43713
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43714
Name     &xThe Webbed Tunnel - Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The stone walls disappear behind layers of thick, white 
silk. The sound of skittering legs is constant, and 
the air is moist and warm.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43715
Desc      The Lair of Maexxna.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43713
Desc      Faerlina's sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43518 10 43714
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43715
Name     &xThe Lair of Maexxna&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The deepest part of the Arachnid Quarter. In the center, 
a gargantuan spider hangs from a massive web suspended 
over a bone-filled pit. Maexxna's red eyes watch 
your every movement with predatory intent.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43714
Desc      The webbed tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT

