Name     &xThe Plague Quarter - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The stone floor is covered in a shallow layer of yellow 
plague-fluid. The air is toxic and smells of rot and 
chemicals. Noth the Plaguebringer can be seen working 
near a massive cauldron ahead.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43741
Desc      The Hall of Noth.~
#ENDEXIT

