#ROOM
Vnum     43741
Name     &xThe Hall of Noth the Plaguebringer&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide circular chamber filled with the remains of the 
plague's victims. Noth stands before a bubbling 
cauldron, chanting over a pile of bones. He summons 
skeletal warriors to defend his work.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43742
Desc      The Gauntlet of Heigan.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
