#ROOM
Vnum     43810
Name     &xThe Construct Quarter - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air here is thick with the scent of chemicals and 
rotting flesh. Massive iron hooks hang from the 
ceiling, and the sound of electric sparks crackles 
through the room.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43811
Desc      The Hall of Patchwerk.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction northeast~
ToRoom    43701
Desc      The central hub.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43520 10 43810
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43811
Name     &xThe Hall of Patchwerk&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive stone hall filled with the remains of 
flesh-crafting experiments. Patchwerk stand in the 
center, his triple arms waving with a mindless 
hunger.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43812
Desc      Toward Grobbulus.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43810
Desc      The construct entry.~
#ENDEXIT

