#ROOM
Vnum     43812
Name     &xThe Lab of Grobbulus&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large room filled with chemical vats and steam pipes. 
Grobbulus stands here, his glass tank bubbling 
with toxic plague-fluid. He sprays a cloud of 
lethal gas to defend his laboratory.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43813
Desc      The Bone-Pile Floor.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43811
Desc      Patchwerk's hall.~
#ENDEXIT

