#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43813
Name     &xThe Bone-Pile of Gluth&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular pit filled with millions of 
 assorted humanoid bones. The skeletal hound 
Gluth stalks the pile, his green eyes glowing 
with hunger as he searches for fresh marrow.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43814
Desc      Toward Thaddius.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43812
Desc      Grobbulus's lab.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 43514 1 43813
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43814
Name     &xThe Tesla Chamber - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Two high stone platforms stand on either side of a 
massive vertical shaft. Enormous copper coils 
pulse with rhythmic electricity, arching 
bolts of blue energy across the gap.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43815
Desc      The Peak of Thaddius.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43813
Desc      Gluth's pit.~
#ENDEXIT

