Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of the Construct Quarter. The 
titanic horror Thaddius stands here, his body 
composed of the flesh of thousands of victims. 
He rumbles with the force of a permanent 
lightning storm, his eyes glowing white.
~
#EXIT
