#ROOM
Vnum     43850
Name     &xThe Upper Necropolis - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive teleporter on the floor of the hub leads 
to the frozen heights of Naxxramas. The air 
here is so cold it hurts to breathe, and the 
walls are coated in a layer of permanent ice.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43851
Desc      The Hall of the Frostwyrm.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    43701
Desc      Return to the hub.~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43851
Name     &xThe Hall of the Frostwyrm&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide circular hall overlooking the open sky. 
The colossal frostwyrm Sapphiron land here, 
his wings casting a wide shadow over the 
frozen floor. He is the final barrier before 
the master.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43852
Desc      The Sanctum of Kel'Thuzad.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43850
