Desc     The absolute heart of Naxxramas. Kel'Thuzad 
floats above a massive stone altar, his hands 
glowing with the icy power of the Lich King. 
The room is filled with the whispers of the 
dead, and the air hums with the final 
destruction of Lordaeron.
~
